cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses the issue of catastrophic forgetting in machine learning and proposes a method to address it. 
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper uses two large-scale computer vision datasets (ImageNet and MS-Celeb-1M) to evaluate the proposed method. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses a problem in AI (catastrophic forgetting) and proposes a solution. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper may involve natural language processing techniques for processing the datasets or discussing related work. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper uses multimedia datasets (images) and may involve multimedia processing techniques for analyzing the datasets.
